{"tid":807653,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去過倫敦嘅你，推薦住喺邊區？","createTime":"2018-09-05T16:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T18:28:41.000Z","uid":205616,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"c05383fcb599a0169e1b35fcf0d99641395106b6","tid":807653,"uid":205616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T16:30:17.000Z","msg":"我book咗機票下年6月去倫敦8日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係仲煩緊住宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己去旅行一般都唔會話住bnb 嗰啲<br />\n因為想舒服啲同安全<br />\n<br />\n依家諗住book 嘅有兩間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩間都係東倫敦<br />\n<br />\nibis budget whitechapel<br />\n呢間喺 Aldgate East 同 Whitechapel 站中間<br />\n挨近Royal London Hospital 嗰邊<br />\n其實我check 過呢區多蝻 好多人都話治安唔係咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢隔離就係清真寺 我擔心夜晚治安唔好<br />\n尢其是係Aldgate East 站返酒店要5分鐘<br />\n但係價錢較平 total &pound;405 <br />\n而且喺Zone 1 2 之間方便安排行程<br />\n<br />\n另一間係 Travelodge London City<br />\n呢間喺正Aldgate 站附近<br />\n雖然附近都係Aldgate 嗰頭但係一上黎就係酒店<br />\n感覺治安相對上好<br />\n但係價錢去到 &pound;507<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實酒店我覺得乾淨就得<br />\n主要考慮治安同交通<br />\n所以想問下去過倫敦嘅巴打們，你會點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07c8a936aafe76ae71b559c90483640f018aea1","tid":807653,"uid":59690,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T16:31:53.000Z","msg":"white chapel都敢住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff965e9d75c8fa382919b58554d05f1ca4db6c36","tid":807653,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T16:31:53.000Z","msg":"一定係西南"},{"pid":"540f38ca042b0b1deccbba9c0de45a8c01