慮治安同交通<br />\n所以想問下去過倫敦嘅巴打們，你會點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T17:16:40.000Z","msg":"酒店早咁多book好貴 早三四個月先book都未遲<br />\n<br />\n你應該冇玩開邊間chain嘅會員啦 如果想住連鎖酒店  可以睇定一至兩條chain 玩埋佢會員可以儲stay儲night 高級啲有唔同benefits upgrade房送早餐之類<br />\n<br />\nibis 就 Accorhotels Group 講真就質素麻麻 係sell平 想book嘅就留意吓佢每年都有幾次叫Private Sale嘅promotion 會有六折至七折"},{"pid":"59f3318c2dacee028272345d0918bc0857cd078e","tid":807653,"uid":41411,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T17:17:55.000Z","msg":"king&rsquo;s cross<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31466443a03141f5cef2b1ea5a27455dd80ace5d","tid":807653,"uid":205616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c33ebd220eb746a04cd4420fafc7c4c18c4e0934","tid":807653,"uid":39678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c05383fcb599a0169e1b35fcf0d99641395106b6","tid":807653,"uid":205616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T16:30:17.000Z","msg":"我book咗機票下年6月去倫敦8日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係仲煩緊住宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己去旅行一般都唔會話住bnb 嗰啲<br />\n因為想舒服啲同安全<br />\n<br />\n依家諗住book 嘅有兩間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩間都係東倫敦<br />\n<br />\nibis budget whitechapel<br />\n呢間喺 Aldgate East 同 Whitechapel 站中間<br />\n挨近Royal London Hospital 嗰邊<br />\n其實我check 過呢區多蝻 好多人都話治安唔係咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢隔離就係清真寺 我擔心夜晚治安唔好<br />\n尢其是係Aldgate East 站返酒店要5分鐘<br />\n但係價錢較平 total &pound;405 <br />\n而且喺Zone 1 2 之間方便安排行程<br />\n<br />\n另一間係 Travelodge London City<br />\n呢間喺正Aldgate 站附近<br />\n雖然附近都係Aldgate 嗰頭但係一上黎就係酒店<br />\n感覺治安相對上好<br />\n但係價錢去到 &pound;507<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" cla