ji\" /> <br />\n但係仲煩緊住宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己去旅行一般都唔會話住bnb 嗰啲<br />\n因為想舒服啲同安全<br />\n<br />\n依家諗住book 嘅有兩間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩間都係東倫敦<br />\n<br />\nibis budget whitechapel<br />\n呢間喺 Aldgate East 同 Whitechapel 站中間<br />\n挨近Royal London Hospital 嗰邊<br />\n其實我check 過呢區多蝻 好多人都話治安唔係咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢隔離就係清真寺 我擔心夜晚治安唔好<br />\n尢其是係Aldgate East 站返酒店要5分鐘<br />\n但係價錢較平 total &pound;405 <br />\n而且喺Zone 1 2 之間方便安排行程<br />\n<br />\n另一間係 Travelodge London City<br />\n呢間喺正Aldgate 站附近<br />\n雖然附近都係Aldgate 嗰頭但係一上黎就係酒店<br />\n感覺治安相對上好<br />\n但係價錢去到 &pound;507<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實酒店我覺得乾淨就得<br />\n主要考慮治安同交通<br />\n所以想問下去過倫敦嘅巴打們，你會點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:08:16.000Z","msg":"Travelodge麻麻地，同ibis一樣似hall多過似inn<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/hotels/articles/revealed-worst-best-hotel-chains-in-britain/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Ftravel%2Fhotels%2Farticles%2Frevealed-worst-best-hotel-chains-in-britain%2Famp%2F&d=v7nfW4n%2FZMB2RpSCwKRmziwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=cf4ad83e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/hotels/articles/revealed-worst-best-hotel-chains-in-britain/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n個人推薦Premier Inn<br />\nFunky d既住Hub by Premier Inn<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前排住過，可以自助check in"},{"pid":"c7e8ea11a6576a3ca4277e296f675319d583b0ac","tid":807653,"uid":197502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53fec0317537fc469d91f1b556857464c36df446","tid":807653,"uid":20609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"re